&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;UiPath&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;User-friendly interface, strong community support&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Can be costly for small businesses&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Zapier&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Integrates with thousands of apps, easy setup&lt;/td&gt;
